and cry to your brother all you like.

544
00:25:21,719 --> 00:25:22,918
There's no one here to spoil you.

545
00:25:22,919 --> 00:25:23,198
Scram!

546
00:25:23,199 --> 00:25:24,839
Why are you mentioning my brother
for no reason?

547
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:25,900
You shrew! Get lost!

548
00:25:25,959 --> 00:25:27,599
- Who are you telling to get lost?
- Say that...

549
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,860
- Look at all the people here.
- Why are you stopping me?

550
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:31,779
Everyone is staring at us.

551
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,159
What are you guys staring at?

552
00:25:36,279 --> 00:25:37,678
Everything's fine.
It's just a misunderstanding.

553
00:25:37,679 --> 00:25:38,819
Who does she think she is?

554
00:25:39,199 --> 00:25:40,660
Why is everyone bullying me?

